			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1334231">
									

<p>Class-A removes recent traumatic memories, makes non-tramatic memories &quot;fuzzy&quot; and leaves you suitable to to suggestion for a brief time.</p>
<p>Class-C tastes like Root Beer.</p>
<p>Seriously, no canon; they do what ever you want. Stories have them doing anything. <a href="/a-man-at-the-top-of-his-profession">Anything At All.</a></p>

