														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1334328">
									

<p>the way i've seen is that it essentially opens a person's mind to be rewritten however the foundation sees fit. if no alterations are made then they just forget the last few hours or days by default(depending on dosage), but if active memory manipulation is used then anything from individual memories to entire years of life could be rewritten.</p>
<p>safe for an unskilled agent to administer in the field and be certain that the person will not remember recent events, but in the hands of trained personnel, capable of any level of memory alteration they wished.</p>

